Integrations
Integrate your tech stack

Switching dialers should never interrupt your workflow, which is why BatchDialer integrates with nearly any software you need to keep your business running smoothly.

Say goodbye to “spam-likely”

Getting flagged as spam can decimate your connection rates, but BatchDialer’s phone reputation technology actively monitors 10+ sources to ensure that you always know the status of your numbers.

Use numbers you can trust

No need to worry about the quality of your numbers. BatchDialer automatically replaces numbers with negative labels so you can focus on having quality conversations with as many prospects as possible.

Eliminate agent downtime

Are your agents making enough connections? Our AI-powered rapid fire mode will turbocharge your dialing by automatically starting a new call as soon as a line becomes available.

Inform your conversations

Have you ever gotten on a call and not known what to say? With BatchDialer, that’s no longer a concern. We provide hyper-accurate property and owner information in the platform.

Avoid the DNC and known litigators

There are a lot of people who don’t want to be called, and you shouldn’t have to manually pick them out of your list. BatchDialer automatically removes known litigators and numbers on the federal do not call registry.

Generate leads quickly

Use BatchDialer Lead Lists to find motivated sellers. Mix and match our 8 different list types at no extra cost.
